00:31:46,933 --> 00:31:50,367
♫ I need you, don't go away ♫

504
00:31:50,367 --> 00:31:53,700
♫ Please don't let go of my hands ♫

505
00:31:53,700 --> 00:31:57,067
♫ I need you, don't go away ♫

506
00:31:57,067 --> 00:32:00,300
♫ It has no other meaning to me ♫

