00:32:08,300 --> 00:32:10,167
♫ I'm standing alone ♫

511
00:32:10,167 --> 00:32:12,433
♫ I can't be with you no more ♫

512
00:32:12,433 --> 00:32:16,033
♫ Our end is coming ♫

